msgstr ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Amministrazione Subversion</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Menu items with administration tasks for subversion repositories like: "
"<simplelist> <member>Create and open new repository</member> <member>Dump "
"repository to file</member> <member>Hotcopy a repository</member> "
"<member>Load dump into repository</member> </simplelist> For more "
"information please read the output of <command>svnadmin --help</command>"
msgstr ""
"Elemento del menu con compiti amministrativi per i depositi di subversion, "
"come: <simplelist> <member>Crea e apri un nuovo deposito</member> "
"<member>Dump del deposito su file</member> <member>Copia a caldo un "
"deposito</member> <member>Carica dump in un deposito</member> </simplelist>. "
"Per ulteriori informazioni leggi l'output di <command>svnadmin --help</"
"command>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1775
#, no-c-format
